<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="affection-n">affection <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'fekʃn/    美 /ə'fekʃn/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>喜爱；钟爱； [常用复数]爱慕；爱情：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>gain / win sb’s affections 
得到某人的爱</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I feel a lot of <strong>affection for</strong> my mother. 
我深爱我的妈妈。</p></div></div>